"{\"uid\": \"salon.com-2024-08-10-why-so-many-olympic-athletes-are-into-cupping-therapy\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"If you have tuned into the summer Olympics in Paris, you may have watched gymnastSimone Biles add another medal to her resum\\u00e9or swimmerKatie Ledecky snag four.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999741112336, \"rank\": 2.5888735208521743e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the summer Olympics\", \"from\": 23, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastSimone Biles\", \"from\": 74, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"another medal\", \"from\": 98, \"to\": 111}, {\"ngram\": \"her resum\\u00e9or swimmerKatie\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 140}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky snag\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have been paying particular attention to swimming, you have also likely noticed some of the athletes' bodies are not only adorned with tattoos but also red and purple circular marks that look like bruises or very large hickeys.\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"particular attention\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 204}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' bodies\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 275}, {\"ngram\": \"tattoos\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"also red and purple circular marks\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"bruises\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"very large hickeys\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, they were not attacked by bugs or animals, but instead, these marks result from a wellness therapy known as \\\"cupping,\\\" or myofascial decompression (MFD).\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multi-function_display\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 1.042465347991053e-11, \"text\": \"MFD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multi-function_display\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Multi-function_display\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bugs\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"animals\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"these marks\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"a wellness therapy\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"cupping\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"myofascial decompression\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Cupping is a common technique utilized to treat soft tissue injuries and increase flexibility,\\\" Neal Stepp, senior athletic trainer at Orlando Health Jewett Orthopedic Institute Performance Health, told Salon, adding there are different techniques.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Health\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Orlando Health\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Health\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orlando_Health\"}, {\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewett_House\", \"score\": 0.7208531357969389, \"rank\": 0.3872450283769261, \"text\": \"Jewett\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewett_House\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewett_House\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.614129110017694e-13, \"text\": \"Salon\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cupping\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"a common technique\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"soft tissue injuries\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"flexibility\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" Neal Stepp\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"senior athletic trainer\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"different techniques\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The most popular cupping technique utilizes a negative pressure soft tissue treatment using suction to manipulate the skin and underlying tissue.\\\"\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most popular cupping technique\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"a negative pressure soft tissue treatment\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"suction\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"underlying tissue\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related Other cupping techniques include utilizing a fire to remove oxygen from the cup causing suction and then utilizing a needle to puncture the skin, suction, and to allegedly release toxins from the punctured skin.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Related Other cupping techniques\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"a fire\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"oxygen\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the cup\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"suction\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"a needle\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"suction\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1114}, {\"ngram\": \"toxins\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"the punctured skin\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Frequently, Stepp said, Olympics athletes experience soft tissue \\\"irritation\\\" or injuries, and one of the several treatments available for this is cupping.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stepp\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics athletes\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"soft tissue \\\"irritation\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"the several treatments\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Athletes who have utilized this technique find it produces great results,\\\" Stepp said.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"this technique\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"great results\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"Stepp\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Other athletes may not find cupping as effective as other soft tissue treatment options.\\\"\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other athletes\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"other soft tissue treatment options\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, he said, the use of cupping depends on the athlete's preferences in treatment along with \\\"accomplishing treatment goals.\\\"\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"cupping\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's preferences\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1587}, {\"ngram\": \"treatment\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"treatment goals\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"By pulling up, it loosens anything tight and stuck, and it draws blood to the area.\\\"\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many athletes swear by it, including Michael Phelps and Olympic gymnastAlex Naddour.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1770, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4119157771302475e-33, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many athletes\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gymnastAlex Naddour\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also been endorsed by celebrities like Gwneyth Paltrow and Jennifer Aniston.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1882, \"end\": 1898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jennifer_Aniston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jennifer Aniston\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jennifer_Aniston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jennifer_Aniston\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"celebrities\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"Gwneyth Paltrow\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being popular among celebrities and athletes, Gudrun Snyder, founder of Moon Rabbit Acupuncture, told Salon cupping is not a new health practice - it's a traditional Chinese medicine practice that has been around for thousands of years.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1954, \"end\": 1960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gudrun\", \"score\": 0.9999999981164365, \"rank\": 1.4856028481207625e-09, \"text\": \"Gudrun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gudrun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gudrun\"}, {\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999999956521606, \"rank\": 4.3360506584012156e-09, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}, {\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.614129110017694e-13, \"text\": \"Salon\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\"}, {\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Traditional_Chinese_medicine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0472248349801892e-20, \"text\": \"traditional Chinese medicine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Traditional_Chinese_medicine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Traditional_Chinese_medicine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"celebrities\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"Moon Rabbit Acupuncture\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"a new health practice\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When cupping in the modern day, Snyder said practitioners usually take a plastic or glass cup as a suction.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2178, \"end\": 2184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999999956521606, \"rank\": 4.3360506584012156e-09, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the modern day\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2176}, {\"ngram\": \"practitioners\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2203}, {\"ngram\": \"a plastic or glass cup\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"a suction\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In more traditional practices, it is used with fire and bamboo cups, as Stepp explained.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more traditional practices\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"fire\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"bamboo cups\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"Stepp\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's similar to massage, where massage pushes down, cupping pulls up on the muscle and the muscles and the fascia that connects the muscles and the connective tissue,\\\" Snyder said.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2513, \"end\": 2519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999999956521606, \"rank\": 4.3360506584012156e-09, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"massage\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2368}, {\"ngram\": \"massage\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscle\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscles\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"the fascia\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"the muscles\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"the connective tissue\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"By pulling up, it loosens anything tight and stuck, and it draws blood to the area.\\\"\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result of the increased blood flow, muscles get looser, and it can help with a range of mobility.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 2616, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"the increased blood flow\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"muscles\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2702}, {\"ngram\": \"mobility\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Swimmers often get a huge build of lactic acid right in their bodies, and they are super sore,\\\" Snyder said.\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2813, \"end\": 2819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999999956521606, \"rank\": 4.3360506584012156e-09, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swimmers\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2725}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge build\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"lactic acid\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"their bodies\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Cupping helps the body to detox that lactic acid and get it moved out of the area so that soreness can be relieved.\\\"\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cupping\", \"from\": 2827, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"the body\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2849}, {\"ngram\": \"that lactic acid\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"that soreness\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Want more health and science stories in your inbox?\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more health and science stories\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe to Salon's weekly newsletterLab Notes.\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3010, \"end\": 3015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.614129110017694e-13, \"text\": \"Salon\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sounds interesting, but what about the bruising?\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bruising\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And does it hurt?\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3113, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snyder said when done right, it should not feel painful.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3114, \"end\": 3120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"score\": 0.9999999956521606, \"rank\": 4.3360506584012156e-09, \"text\": \"Snyder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ted_Snyder\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"right\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But one might feel a bit of a \\\"pinch.\\\"\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3178}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"pinch\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It might feel \\\"funny,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As if you are being \\\"hugged by an octopus.\\\"\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an octopus\", \"from\": 3275, \"to\": 3285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite anecdotal evidence from some of the world's best athletes, it's natural to wonder if it's just a placebo effect or if there is real science to support this wellness.\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anecdotal evidence\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best athletes\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3354}, {\"ngram\": \"just a placebo effect\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3408}, {\"ngram\": \"real science\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"this wellness\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One 2013 study published in the journalPLOS Oneexamined 61 people, finding those with chronic neck pain reported reductions in pain after 12 weeks of treatment.\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One 2013 study\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3477}, {\"ngram\": \"the journalPLOS\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3506}, {\"ngram\": \"61 people\", \"from\": 3519, \"to\": 3528}, {\"ngram\": \"chronic neck pain reported reductions\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3586}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3594}, {\"ngram\": \"12 weeks\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3609}, {\"ngram\": \"treatment\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When compared to a cohort of people who used a technique called Progressive Muscle Relaxation (PMR), the cupping group reported less pain in the affected area when pressure was applied.\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cohort\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3649}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3659}, {\"ngram\": \"a technique\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3680}, {\"ngram\": \"Progressive Muscle Relaxation\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3717}, {\"ngram\": \"(PMR\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"the cupping group\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3742}, {\"ngram\": \"less pain\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3761}, {\"ngram\": \"the affected area\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3782}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 3788, \"to\": 3796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Cupping massage may however be better than PMR in improving well-being and decreasing pressure pain sensitivity but more studies with larger samples and longer follow-up periods are needed to confirm these results,\\\" the researchers concluded.\", \"from\": 3810, \"to\": 4053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cupping massage\", \"from\": 3811, \"to\": 3826}, {\"ngram\": \"PMR\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3857}, {\"ngram\": \"well-being and decreasing pressure pain sensitivity\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 3922}, {\"ngram\": \"more studies\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3939}, {\"ngram\": \"larger samples\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3959}, {\"ngram\": \"longer follow-up periods\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 3988}, {\"ngram\": \"these results\", \"from\": 4011, \"to\": 4024}, {\"ngram\": \"the researchers\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In aseparate 2012 study, researchers found that people who had arthritis in their knees and underwent cupping reported less pain in 16 weeks compared to those who did not receive any treatment.\", \"from\": 4055, \"to\": 4248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aseparate 2012 study\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4078}, {\"ngram\": \"researchers\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4091}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4109}, {\"ngram\": \"arthritis\", \"from\": 4118, \"to\": 4127}, {\"ngram\": \"their knees\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4142}, {\"ngram\": \"less pain\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4183}, {\"ngram\": \"16 weeks\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4195}, {\"ngram\": \"any treatment\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In this exploratory study dry cupping with a pulsatile cupping device relieved symptoms of knee OA compared to no intervention,\\\" the researchers said.\", \"from\": 4249, \"to\": 4400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pulsatile cupping device\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4319}, {\"ngram\": \"relieved symptoms\", \"from\": 4320, \"to\": 4337}, {\"ngram\": \"knee OA\", \"from\": 4341, \"to\": 4348}, {\"ngram\": \"no intervention\", \"from\": 4361, \"to\": 4376}, {\"ngram\": \"the researchers\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Further studies comparing cupping with active treatments are needed.\\\"\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Further studies\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"active treatments\", \"from\": 4441, \"to\": 4458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this year, a systematic review in the journalComplementary Therapies in Medicineexamined 11 studies related to cupping effectiveness and reported \\\"high- to moderate-quality evidence that cupping significantly improves pain and disability.\\\"\", \"from\": 4473, \"to\": 4720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a systematic review\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4511}, {\"ngram\": \"the journalComplementary Therapies\", \"from\": 4515, \"to\": 4549}, {\"ngram\": \"Medicineexamined 11 studies\", \"from\": 4553, \"to\": 4580}, {\"ngram\": \"cupping effectiveness\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4613}, {\"ngram\": \"high-\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4633}, {\"ngram\": \"moderate-quality evidence\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4662}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 4699, \"to\": 4703}, {\"ngram\": \"disability\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The authors even said \\\"cupping surpasses medication and usual care in reducing pain.\\\"\", \"from\": 4721, \"to\": 4806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The authors\", \"from\": 4721, \"to\": 4732}, {\"ngram\": \"surpasses medication\", \"from\": 4752, \"to\": 4772}, {\"ngram\": \"usual care\", \"from\": 4777, \"to\": 4787}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need your help to stay in